PrecisAppointment of SERGE LAVALLﾃ右, of Montreal, Quebec, as a full-time member of the National Parole Board, Quebec Regional Division, to hold office during good behaviour for a period of seven years; and designation of SERGE LAVALLﾃ右 as Vice-Chairperson for the Quebec region of the National Parole Board, in the place of Keith Morgan.
